phase2.explanation:
UI references need to be assigned in the Inspector.

**The fix:**
```csharp
void Start()
{
    if (scoreText != null)
        scoreText.text = "Score: 0";
    else
        Debug.LogError("scoreText is not assigned!");
}
```

**Sharp-chan says:**
"Always assign UI references in the Inspector."
